-- Brenntag Buys EAC Industrial Ingredients for $201 Million to Grow in Asia
-- Angela Cullen
-- 2010-07-05T05:41:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-05/brenntag-buys-eac-industrial-ingredients-for-201-million-to-grow-in-asia.html

          
          
             Brenntag AG, the German chemicals 
distributor owned by BC Partners Ltd., agreed to buy EAS
Industrial Ingredients Ltd. A/S for 160 million euros ($201
million) to expand its chemical distributions operations in
Asia.  
          
          


  


        